text_content: I love spending time alone and thinking deeply about new ideas.
I'm always on the go and love meeting new people.
Organization and discipline help me achieve my goals.
I often feel worried or anxious even without a clear reason.
I enjoy helping others and being part of a cooperative team.
Creativity and imagination are at the heart of everything I do.
I prefer to follow rules and keep everything in order.
Social gatherings energize me and I love making new friends.
I sometimes struggle with self-doubt and overthinking.
Kindness and empathy guide my interactions with others.
